<view class="page wallet-recharge-page"><view class="form-header"><view class="form-header-title">在线支付充值</view><view class="form-header-desc">选择要充值的账户类型，并完成微信模拟支付扣款。</view></view><view class="section"><view class="section-title">账户选择 <text class="required">*</text></view><view class="grid-two"><view class="{{['check-row', b && 'checked']}}" bindtap="{{c}}"><text class="radio-icon-box">{{a}}</text><text>保证金账户</text></view><view class="{{['check-row', e && 'checked']}}" bindtap="{{f}}"><text class="radio-icon-box">{{d}}</text><text>信息服务费账户</text></view></view></view><view class="section"><view class="section-title">充值金额 <text class="required">*</text></view><view class="presets-grid"><view wx:for="{{g}}" wx:for-item="amt" wx:key="b" class="{{['preset-item', 'font-bold', amt.c && 'active']}}" bindtap="{{amt.d}}">{{amt.a}}元 </view></view><view class="field" style="margin-top:30rpx"><text class="label">自定义充值金额 (元)</text><input class="input" type="digit" placeholder="请输入充值金额" placeholder-style="color:#9ca3af" value="{{h}}" bindinput="{{i}}"/></view></view><view class="fixed-footer"><button class="primary-btn animate-btn w-full" loading="{{j}}" bindtap="{{k}}"> 确认充值 (模拟微信支付) </button></view></view>